After a very long time, exim bank has introduced a usable and modern app which supports all the necessary functions for online banking. But it seems each function is taking longer than usual to load properly. A banking app should be fast, fluid and reliable like city touch and dbbl banking app. If this issue is fixed, i will review my rating and provide 4 star. Also i suggest removing the Exim eWallet app from the play store because that's unusable and outdated by atleast 4 years. Thanks
